## Try It Yourself

Dockyy is open-source and ready to deploy. With Bun, UV, and modern tooling, setup takes just a few minutes:

**üîó GitHub Repository**: [github.com/rifkyputra/dockyy](https://github.com/rifkyputra/dockyy)

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/rifkyputra/dockyy.git
cd dockyy

# Backend setup
cd backend
uv sync
python migrate.py upgrade
uv run python -m app

# Frontend setup (in another terminal)
cd frontend
bun install
bun run dev
```

Point your browser to `http://localhost:3000`, and you're ready to manage your Docker infrastructure from a beautiful, modern dashboard.

